"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_DDANTUMBRA_HURTLIGHT\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/text"
msgstr "尽管冥影位面如今恢复的色彩汹涌而至，带着宁静的美感……不知为何，你却不禁被这随"
