" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"……天啊，这里有好多光裔族！他们似乎也没有受到虚伪辉光的影响……如果你，呃，愿意"
"的话，或许可以利用我姐姐的存在激怒其中一些？这可能会引来不必要的注意，但……也"
"可能引来我们想要的注意！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:1321
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_DDANTUMBRA_ANXIOUSBORNE\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "想象一份协定——正是那份拟定计划所达成的协定。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:1323
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_DDANTUMBRA_ANXIOUSBORNE\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"不过他们的数量确实很多……这里有这么多光裔族，你得把她的信号再增强一些，越过那"
"些弱小个体，才能传达到强大的目标那里。是否值得冒这个险，呃……由你决定。那些弱"
"小的光裔族，呃……以它们自己的方式来说，也同样不容小觑！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:1325
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_DDANTUMBRA_ANXIOUSBORNE\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "想象风险——那种因吸引注意力而伴随的风险。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:1329
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_DDANTUMBRA_ANXIOUSBORNE\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "想象安全——那种在边缘地带寻得的安稳。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:1335
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_DDANTUMBRA_ANXIOUSBORNE\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "想象犹豫——一种因身处危险而产生的谨慎。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:1337
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_DDANTUMBRA_ANXIOUSBORNE\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"好吧，如果你愿意的话，你可以让她在边缘这里吸引一些较弱的光裔族的注意。这么做"
"应该不会有太大风险，呃……就算有也微乎其微！我感觉更强的光裔族在群体更深处，需"
"要使用可能更危险的信号强度才行，不过……这真的由你决定！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:1339
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_DDANTUMBRA_ANXIOUSBORNE\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
