"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_DDANTUMBRA_INFIGHTING_LIST_BREAKCINDER\"]/choice[@req=\"DDFALSERADIANCE_RADIANT_CORE_TIERONE_CINDERLING\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"这……真是个有意思的想法。或许不用把它们引诱到飞船上，你可以用你的辉光核心把烬"
"灵族引开？这样一来，碎灵族就能使用这里的空间，而烬灵族也能在别处拥有属于它们"
"自己的地盘！不错，呃……真是个好主意，我！我觉得……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:1591
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_DDANTUMBRA_INFIGHTING_LIST_BREAKCINDER\"]/choice[@req=\"DDFALSERADIANCE_RADIANT_CORE_TIERONE_CINDERLING\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "想象一个更遥远的地方——那是光的归宿。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:1597
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_DDANTUMBRA_INFIGHTING_LIST_BREAKCINDER\"]/choice[3]/text"
msgstr "想象一把锤子——一只碎灵，绝望地困在某人的飞船上。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:1599
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_DDANTUMBRA_INFIGHTING_LIST_BREAKCINDER\"]/choice[3]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"我不确定这有多符合道义，但是……现在我姐姐需要帮助，而且没时间让那些仍受她控制"
"的光裔族争吵不休了！要把它们引诱过来，其实只需要一次干脆的，呃……撞击？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:1604
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_DDANTUMBRA_INFIGHTING_LIST_BREAKCINDER\"]/choice[3]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "想象一头撞角巨兽——雄壮、炽烈、高声嘶鸣！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:1606
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_DDANTUMBRA_INFIGHTING_LIST_BREAKCINDER\"]/choice[3]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "哦，哇，呃——来了，它们来了！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:1613
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_DDANTUMBRA_INFIGHTING_LIST_BREAKCINDER\"]/choice[4]/text"
msgstr "想象一团火焰——一只烬灵，绝望地困在某人的飞船上。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:1615
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_DDANTUMBRA_INFIGHTING_LIST_BREAKCINDER\"]/choice[4]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"我不确定这是否合乎道义，但是……现在我姐姐需要帮助，而且没时间让那些仍受她控制"
"的光裔族争吵不休了！要把它们引诱过来，其实只需要一次干脆的，呃……撞击？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:1620
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_DDANTUMBRA_INFIGHTING_LIST_BREAKCINDER\"]/choice[4]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "想象一头撞角巨兽——雄壮、炽烈、高声嘶鸣！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:1622
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_DDANTUMBRA_INFIGHTING_LIST_BREAKCINDER\"]/choice[4]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "哦，哇，呃——来了，它们来了！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:1629
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_DDANTUMBRA_INFIGHTING_LIST_BREAKCINDER\"]/choice[5]/text"
msgstr "想象一个出口——一条脱离这场交涉的出路。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:1631
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_DDANTUMBRA_INFIGHTING_LIST_BREAKCINDER\"]/choice[5]/event/text"
msgstr "哦，呃……这也说得通！光裔族早晚都会搞明白他们自己那些奇奇怪怪的事，对吧？你只"
"需要，你知道的……继续航行！航行着，还有，嗯……自在前行……？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:1633
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_DDANTUMBRA_INFIGHTING_LIST_BREAKCINDER\"]/choice[5]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "想象一件琐碎的差事——一件在闲暇时去完成的事。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:1637
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_DDANTUMBRA_INFIGHTING_LIST_BREAKCINDER\"]/choice[5]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "想象虚无——那终有一天会包容万物的存在。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:1645
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_DDANTUMBRA_INFIGHTING\"]/text"
msgstr "..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:1648
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_DDANTUMBRA_INFIGHTING\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/text"
msgstr "..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:1650
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_DDANTUMBRA_INFIGHTING\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"……这地方看起来真是挤满了东西，对吧？看来你无意间闯进了一处低级光裔族的繁衍之"
"地……而且这里也从未被虚伪辉光沾染过！应该不会太麻烦，你知道的……让我姐姐稍微唤"
"醒它们一下，看看它们能不能，嗯，以某种方式帮帮你？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:1652
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_DDANTUMBRA_INFIGHTING\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "想象一个清晨——人类与光明一同归来。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:1654
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_DDANTUMBRA_INFIGHTING\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"哦，它们没有……吗？它，呃……它们看起来根本没在听她的信号。这种情况很少见，但……"
"也不是从未有过。有时候，光裔族会陷入盲目、争夺领地的冲突——两种不同的光裔族会"
"互相争斗，直到一方最终胜出，赢得这片空间。到了这个地步，在舍弃了生命中更美好"
"的乐趣之后，光裔族真正在乎的就只有繁衍……所以我姐姐会，呃……发现它们处于这种状"
"态，也不算太令人意外。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:1656
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_DDANTUMBRA_INFIGHTING\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "想象一场争端——或许是一场即将了结的争端。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:1660
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_DDANTUMBRA_INFIGHTING\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "想象一种漠然——一种对野兽间权谋毫无兴趣的漠然。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:1662
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_DDANTUMBRA_INFIGHTING\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你就随它们自顾自地古怪下去好了，是啊……反正它们无视我姐姐，也实在有点没礼貌，"
"不是吗？她明明是想保护它们啊！或者至少，她……呃……她本来会保护它们的，如果她……"
"\n"
"\n"
"……我真的很希望一切都能顺利解决。希望我姐姐没事，然后我们就能……我们就能回到以"
"前的样子，回到伪辉光出现之前，回到那面……镜子出现之前。可是，呃！我、呃……我不"
"是故意要把气氛搞糟的！那个，你知道的，呃——如果你需要什么就告诉我，好吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:1666
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_DDANTUMBRA_INFIGHTING\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "想象一件琐碎的差事——一件在闲暇时去完成的事。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:1670
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_DDANTUMBRA_INFIGHTING\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "想象虚无——那终有一天会包容万物的存在。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:1680
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_DDANTUMBRA_INFIGHTING\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/text"
msgstr "..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:1682
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_DDANTUMBRA_INFIGHTING\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/text"
msgstr "尽管冥影位面如今恢复的色彩汹涌而至，带着宁静的美感……不知为何，你却不禁被这随"
"之而来的寂静所困扰。这里似乎已经没有什么值得你留恋的了。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:1685
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_DDANTUMBRA_INFIGHTING\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "星舰管理。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:1689
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_DDANTUMBRA_INFIGHTING\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "跳过。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:1698
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//ship[@name=\"NEUTRAL_DDANTUMBRA_SUBTERFUGE_FIGHT\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr ""
"看起来那些爆炸物和舰队一起，呃……在你战斗的时候飘走了。考虑到它们当时正忙着搞"
"些小动作，这倒不算特别意外，不过……至少你在一定程度上打乱了虚伪辉光的计划！胜"
"利就是胜利，不是吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:1712
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_DDANTUMBRA_SUBTERFUGE_MADDASH_LIST_CAUGHT\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"等等，小——\n"
"\n"
"……心。它们绝对，呃……它们绝对看见你了！你必须保护好自己，在它们发动更多攻击之"
"前！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:1723
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_DDANTUMBRA_SUBTERFUGE_MADDASH_LIST_CAUGHT\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "想象战斗——一种需要时刻准备的行为。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:1729
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_DDANTUMBRA_SUBTERFUGE_UNDERWAY\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"哇，干得漂亮——这居然真的奏效了！你已经到了它们的爆炸物堆旁……一大堆不稳定的术"
"士结晶，随时都可能引爆。它们已经被虚伪辉光腐化了，所以我不会，呃……太在意把它"
"们引爆。这有点令人难过，但是……至少它们还能派上用场，对吧？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:1731
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_DDANTUMBRA_SUBTERFUGE_UNDERWAY\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "想象一枚临时制作的爆炸物——已被动手脚，准备引发连锁反应。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:1733
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_DDANTUMBRA_SUBTERFUGE_UNDERWAY\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr "现在，你只需要快点离开那里！在虚伪辉光，呃……发、发现之前！或者，你知道的……在"
"术士结晶爆炸之前？！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:1738
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_DDANTUMBRA_SUBTERFUGE_UNDERWAY\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "想象距离——那种此刻迫切需要的距离。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:1740
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_DDANTUMBRA_SUBTERFUGE_UNDERWAY\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"随时都会——哦！好啊，尝尝这个，你们，呃……你们这些邪恶的混蛋！这是为我姐姐和她"
"的容器报仇！不是说她之后，呃……不能亲自报仇，只是，呃……无论如何！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:1744
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_DDANTUMBRA_SUBTERFUGE_UNDERWAY\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "想象报应——一份被折射千倍的痛苦馈赠。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:1746
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_DDANTUMBRA_SUBTERFUGE_UNDERWAY\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "虚伪辉光已被解决，他们的战利品任由你取！此外，你摧毁了他们的舰队与炸药储藏，"
"沉重打击了他们的阴谋……干得漂亮，你！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:1750
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_DDANTUMBRA_SUBTERFUGE_UNDERWAY\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "想象满足感——圆满完成任务后的真正奖赏。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:1752
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_DDANTUMBRA_SUBTERFUGE_UNDERWAY\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"不过我还是忍不住想知道它们的计划到底是什么……那些术士结晶的威力足以把大天使炸"
"入地狱。倒不是说它们真的会这么做，只是……我就是觉得有点担心，你明白吗？我姐姐"
"从未见过光裔族独自策划这样的事情。不过，只要你，呃……保持警惕，我相信一切都会"
"好起来的！至少我希望如此……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:1762
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_DDANTUMBRA_SUBTERFUGE_UNDERWAY\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "想象一个难题——前路无路可走。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:1764
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_DDANTUMBRA_SUBTERFUGE_UNDERWAY\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "……哦。那，呃……确实是个问题，不是吗？我想你可以直接自己朝储藏库开火，但是……那"
"听起来很危险，不是吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:1766
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_DDANTUMBRA_SUBTERFUGE_UNDERWAY\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[@req=\"weapons\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/text"
msgstr "想象危险——在这样的时代，危险是必要的。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:1768
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_DDANTUMBRA_SUBTERFUGE_UNDERWAY\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[@req=\"weapons\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/text"
msgstr "好啦，只是……啊……至少稍微拉开点距离，好吗？你的飞船会被擦到一点，但应该不算太"
"严重。不过这……感觉还是有点疯狂啊……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:1770
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_DDANTUMBRA_SUBTERFUGE_UNDERWAY\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[@req=\"weapons\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "想象一场爆炸——即将来袭、迫在眉睫、无处可逃。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:1772
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_DDANTUMBRA_SUBTERFUGE_UNDERWAY\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[@req=\"weapons\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"这一切真的在发生……好吧，我很冷静，我、我……\n"
"\n"
"……等等，居、居然没事？！居、居然真的成功了！好耶，接招吧，你们、呃……你们这群"
"混蛋！这是为我姐姐和她的座驾讨回公道！虽然她、啊……之后也能亲自报仇，但、呃……"
"不管怎样！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:1781
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"NEUTRAL_DDANTUMBRA_SUBTERFUGE_UNDERWAY\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[@req=\"weapons\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
