msgstr "想象一位光裔族——获得新生，化作机械之躯。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:2040
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_DDANTUMBRA_RESOURCES\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
