"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"没有掘墓者的介入，他们还不算真正活着，但……这已经是我姐姐在此期间能做到的最好"
"结果了。希望他们，呃……能好好为你效力？至少在他们真正的转世得以解决之前！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:2045
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_DDANTUMBRA_RESOURCES\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
