msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_DDANTUMBRA_ANCIENTWRECK_GAMBLE_SLOW\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"……呃，这都过了多久了？我才不管这烂摊子是谁的——为什么这里非得……这么……几何化、"
"还这么对称啊？感觉明明到处都找遍了，却像是在同一个区域里绕了好几个小时！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:2164
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_DDANTUMBRA_ANCIENTWRECK_GAMBLE_SLOW\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "体悟耐心——此等时局下的美德。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:2166
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"ITEMS_DDANTUMBRA_ANCIENTWRECK_GAMBLE_SLOW\"]/choice/event/text"
