msgstr "你……？你以为我……等等，创世之源要走了？！给我回来，你……你，呃……唉，算了。刚才"
"我明明都在发抖，现在还要装强硬，真的很难……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:2972
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_SHATTEREDMEMORY\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "想象一场调查——很少有人会漫无目的地徘徊。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:2974
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_SHATTEREDMEMORY\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "哦，呃……我想你说得对。就算它跑了，我们或许也能弄清楚它为什么会在这里……只不过"
"，嗯……我实在感觉不到有什么不对劲的地方。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:2976
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_SHATTEREDMEMORY\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "想象一道信号——一次试图看见无形之物的尝试。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:2978
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_SHATTEREDMEMORY\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"嗯，你说得对——如果说有谁能在冥影位面里找到蛛丝马迹，那一定是我姐姐。我会让她"
"的容器发出信号，然后……\n"
"\n"
"……等、等一下，那是……？我……我还以为那是……哦，父亲——求您，庇佑我们。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:2982
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_SHATTEREDMEMORY\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "想象一段阐释——简洁扼要，以防时间紧迫。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:2984
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_SHATTEREDMEMORY\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"是……那面镜子。就是我姐姐……那、那面被创世之源……啊……它一定是把镜子带到了这里，"
"藏了起来，然后……可、可是为什么？难道……它有什么想看见的东西吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:2986
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_SHATTEREDMEMORY\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "想象一道目光——一种敏锐的感知，献给那些拥有感知之力的存在。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:2988
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_SHATTEREDMEMORY\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "你……你觉得我应该……好吧，如果我姐姐都这么做了，我……我想这应该没什么坏处。也许"
"我能看见，到底是什么东西让创世之源如此迫切地想要看见……？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:2990
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_SHATTEREDMEMORY\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/text"
msgstr "窥见真相——即便被镜面所遮蔽。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:2992
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_SHATTEREDMEMORY\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/text"
msgstr "真相？我……呃……我不明白你是什么意思。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:2994
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_SHATTEREDMEMORY\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/text"
msgstr "想象一瞥——第一次，窥见现实。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:2996
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_SHATTEREDMEMORY\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"好了，好了！我这就看！只是……\n"
"\n"
"……里面只有我而已，你知道吗？或者至少……是我姐姐曾经看见的那个我。是她。或者，"
"呃……是我。只……只是……这里面为什么这么黑？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:3000
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_SHATTEREDMEMORY\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
