"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/text"
msgstr "想象那血——是比漆黑更黑的猩红之貌。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:3002
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_SHATTEREDMEMORY\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/text"
msgstr "你到底是……？我……我听不懂你在说什么。我没有流血，什么都没有——只是……很黑，好吗"
"？不管这里是哪里，就是很黑。仅此而已。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:3004
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_SHATTEREDMEMORY\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/text"
msgstr "想象一段记忆——破碎不堪，却并未彻底毁灭。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:3006
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_SHATTEREDMEMORY\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"我……我以前来过这里吗……？不……不会的，这样的地方我一定会记得。我一定会记得，如"
"果……如果……等等，我到底能记住些什么……？我的两个姐姐，我们和父亲一同度过的时光"
"，我所有的梦想……可是，真的就没有别的了吗？难道……从来就没有过别的吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:3008
