"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/text"
msgstr "想象家人——那不可或缺，却又偏偏被遗忘的存在。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:3010
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_SHATTEREDMEMORY\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"母……母亲！我当然……其实不是的——我们谁都没有真正……呃……认识她，真的没有……我是说"
"，除了父亲之外。可我……我的确会梦见她。不只是她，还有……很多很多东西，反复出现"
"。一张张面孔，绿色的虚影，金色的田野……还有那永恒的、猩红的黑夜……等、等一下，"
"你……你刚才是不是也提到过类似的事情？你怎么会……我……我，呃……我觉得我们应该带上"
"镜子，离开这里。说实话，我现在……嗯……感觉很不舒服。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:3012
