" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"你根本连一半都不知道，妹妹……不过没关系。很快你就会看清全部的真相，我的容器会"
"确保这一切。而当你真正明白时……我会在我们曾经的家——那座牢笼，那座坟墓里，等着"
"你们三个。"

