"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_SHATTEREDMEMORY\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/text"
msgstr "你要是愿意，就安静点——这无关紧要。不过，如果你不想让他失望……就配合一下，好吗"
"？他肯定会很讨厌你变得如此消沉，而他的预案也因此失败……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:3048
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_SHATTEREDMEMORY\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"配……配合？我……我，呃……我不想让父亲失望。我会……我会，只是……好的。那……那面镜子"
"！我们，呃……我们要把它带到起源之地，对吧？为了拯救冥影位面，还有我……我的姐姐…"
"…"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:3050
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_SHATTEREDMEMORY\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"真是个乖巧听话的好孩子……也难怪我们当初会任人摆布。不过没关系……他们的报应迟早"
"会来。父亲自然会是第一个。然后，就轮到他……直到最后，所有人都能加入这场狂欢。"
"哦，那会是多么有趣的场面……他们都会明白，真正的痛苦究竟意味着什么。在永恒的折"
"磨中扭曲、挣扎、癫狂……永远无法逃离那片猩红。但我不该操之过急——还有许多景象尚"
"未呈现。在此期间……没错，容器——那面镜子。你要去的地方，正需要它。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:3052
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_SHATTEREDMEMORY\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\"]/event/text"
msgstr "我们……呃，走吧，哈哈！起源之地在等着我们……！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:3086
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_SHATTEREDMEMORY\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/text"
msgstr "映照出一段倒影——那等待被看见的存在。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:3088
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_SHATTEREDMEMORY\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"好吧，那——开始了！我看看……\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"……哦。原来……那就是我吗？我，呃……看起来确实不怎么光鲜了，哈哈。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:3094
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_SHATTEREDMEMORY\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "想象一份关切——专注于细节，尤为如此。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:3096
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_SHATTEREDMEMORY\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"嗯，我……我和我姐姐当年的样子一模一样。这并不是真正的我，就像她的倒影也不是真"
"正的她一样，可是……我想这就是我们一直以来想象中自己的模样。唯一的不同是，呃……"
"我所在的这个地方要阴暗得多，而且我看起来，啊……我想，是太疲惫了吧？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:3098
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_SHATTEREDMEMORY\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "想象一个房间——必然会有具体的形态描绘。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:3100
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_SHATTEREDMEMORY\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"就是这样，真的——这里一片漆黑。说真的，我……呃，你也知道，如果没有属于自己的容"
"器，我几乎无法动弹，也看不见周围的事物。而既然父亲选择不给我容器，我通常就只"
"能待在他身边……可、可正是这一点让我对现在的处境感到无比恐惧。我以前从来没有迷"
"失过，也从来没有孤身一人过……先不去管我到底在哪里、又是怎么来到这里的——天父怎"
"么会把我弄丢？这是一场意外，还是……这一切都是他计划好的？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:3102
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_SHATTEREDMEMORY\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "想象那些奥秘——无穷无尽，却或许不会永远如此。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:3104
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_SHATTEREDMEMORY\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"darkone_alignment\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"好的，呃……等我姐姐恢复正常后，也许她可以去和父亲谈谈，让他把这一团乱麻理清。"
"你或许也可以去和他说说？我其实，啊……也不太确定，可是……至少只要我还能和姐姐保"
"持这种联系，我就不会觉得完全迷失了。很大程度上也是因为我能和你说话！以一种很"
"奇妙的，你知道的……单向半沟通的方式。\n"
"\n"
"不过说句题外话——我觉得光是盯着这面镜子，我们得不到太多信息。但我想你可以把它"
"带上，你永远不知道之后什么时候它就会派上用场……！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:3117
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_SHATTEREDMEMORY\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[3]/text"
msgstr "想象黑暗——一种弥漫于视野之中的失明感。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:3119
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_SHATTEREDMEMORY\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[3]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"我……呃……是啊，你说得或许没错。如果这面镜子里所映照出的东西，曾经侵蚀过起源之"
"地，那么现在去看它，可能依然存在风险。但无论如何……我觉得你至少应该把它带上——"
"你永远不知道之后什么时候它就会派上用场……！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:3136
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_SHATTEREDMEMORY\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/text"
msgstr "..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:3138
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_SHATTEREDMEMORY\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/text"
msgstr "尽管冥影位面如今已恢复的色彩汹涌而至，带着宁静的美好……不知为何，你却不禁被它"
"们留下的寂静所困扰。这里似乎已经没有什么值得你留恋的了。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:3141
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_SHATTEREDMEMORY\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "星舰管理。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:3145
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_SHATTEREDMEMORY\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "跳过。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:3154
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//ship[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_GRAVEDIGGERLOCATION_FIGHT\"]/destroyed/text"
msgstr "你竟然又设法打败了一位大天使……你、你真的太了不起了，不是吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:3157
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//ship[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_GRAVEDIGGERLOCATION_FIGHT\"]/destroyed/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_DDTHESHADEFORMS\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/text"
msgstr "想象一场胜利——来之不易，却更令人期盼。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:3161
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//ship[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_GRAVEDIGGERLOCATION_FIGHT\"]/destroyed/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_DDTHESHADEFORMS\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/text"
msgstr "想象一场胜利——浴血奋战而来，更被热切期盼。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:3168
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"START_DDANTUMBRA_THEGRAVEDIGGER_FIGHT_WIN\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"掌控死亡的力量，以及恢复能量的能力……我简直不敢相信你又做到了！我的姐姐也可以"
"吸收这位掘墓者的力量……这不仅是她的胜利，也是起源之地的挫败。它正变得越来越虚"
"弱，而我们却在不断变强！或者，呃……你懂的，是你。是、是她在变强。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:3171
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"START_DDANTUMBRA_THEGRAVEDIGGER_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "想象力量——它是危机时刻的必需之物，却也常常正是制造危机的元凶。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:3173
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"START_DDANTUMBRA_THEGRAVEDIGGER_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"对于掘墓者而言，腐朽是可憎之物——正因如此，当你掌控这份力量后，你的同伴们在你"
"的护盾、引擎或武器控制室中时，会随时间逐渐恢复生命，每个房间的治愈速度会随着"
"注入的力量提升而加快。不仅如此……只要待在这些房间里，他们光是站着就能自然地为"
"你提供少量能量！这难道不是，呃……太、太了不起了吗？！\n"
"\n"
"至少我，呃……我希望是这样。父亲很清楚，如果你要对抗起源之地，你需要一切能得到"
"的帮助……可、可是！我对你和我姐姐充满信心！我知道你们一定能做到，就算其他人都"
"做不到——所以抬起头来，好吗？只要我们还在，你就不是孤身一人。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:3179
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"START_DDANTUMBRA_THEGRAVEDIGGER_FIGHT_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "想象一段旅程——纵使前路仍有重重考验，也必须继续前行。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:3187
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"START_DDANTUMBRA_THEGRAVEDIGGER_FIGHT_WIN_DEATH\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"我不太担心我姐姐的容器。每击败一位大天使，都会留下足够多的残余力量让她自我修"
"复。呃，说到力量！完全掌控死亡，还有恢复能量的能力……我简直不敢相信你又做到了"
"！我姐姐也能吸收这股掘墓者的力量……这不仅是她的胜利，也是起源之地的损失。它只"
"会越来越弱，而我们则越来越强！或者，呃……你懂的，是你。是、是她在变强。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:3189
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"START_DDANTUMBRA_THEGRAVEDIGGER_FIGHT_WIN_DEATH\"]/crewMember"
msgstr "暗影"

