"只 为\n"
"渴 求\n"
"一 场\n"
"幻 梦？\n"
"\n"
"只 为\n"
"执 守\n"
"一 份\n"
"无 助\n"
"的\n"
"希 望？\n"
"\n"
"而 你，\n"
"旁 观 者……\n"
"\n"
"你\n"
"究 竟\n"
"想\n"
"通 过\n"
"封 印\n"
"我 们\n"
"的\n"
"命 运，\n"
"获 得\n"
"什 么？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:3888
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "想象那未知——一种莫名的牵引，让人不断前行。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:3890
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"所 以，\n"
"连 你\n"
"也 无 法\n"
"确 定\n"
"自 己 的\n"
"所 作 所 为……\n"
"\n"
"我 们\n"
"只 是\n"
"希 望，\n"
"就 算\n"
"碾 碎\n"
"我 们\n"
"自 己 的\n"
"梦 想……\n"
"\n"
"你\n"
"或 许\n"
"终 将\n"
"明 白\n"
"你 的\n"
"心 愿。\n"
"\n"
"再 见 了，\n"
"旁 观 者。\n"
"\n"
"请\n"
"代 我 们\n"
"向 她\n"
"问 好……\n"
"\n"
"等 待\n"
"她\n"
"跳 完\n"
"那 场\n"
"注 定 的\n"
"舞 时。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:3936
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "想象一场告别——神性的终焉，正如光裔族所知的那样。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:3938
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:3942
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:3944
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"……随着大天使协议：创世纪自行销毁，其力量得以释放……你感受着那股神圣能量冲刷着"
"你的舰船，一种久违的安稳感重新回到你身上。视觉、触觉、嗅觉——甚至你的思考能力…"
"…在一瞬间，全都涌回你的体内。你先是一阵惊愕——但随即，你看见了它们。冥影位面那"
"早已失落许久的色彩……至少，你曾听过的故事是这么说的。那套灌输给你的谎言……当此"
"地发生的一切沉重地压向你时，房间角落里的一道阴影，悄然吸引了你的目光。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:3950
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_DDTHESHADEFORMS\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/text"
msgstr "尽全力集中你的视线。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:3952
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_DDTHESHADEFORMS\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你摆脱昏沉，立刻认出了那个身影——那是影使残破不堪、伤痕累累的躯体。据说，她是"
"那个羞怯声音的姐姐的容器……是你脑海中那个早已失声哭泣的失踪少女。清醒过来后，"
"你才更清楚地明白，创世纪协议早先称呼她为——一面盾牌。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:3954
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_DDTHESHADEFORMS\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "我以前在哪里听过这个……？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:3960
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_DDTHESHADEFORMS\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/text"
msgstr "尽全力集中你的视线。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:3962
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_DDTHESHADEFORMS\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你驱散了脑中的昏沉，很快辨认出那个身影——是幽影，依旧带着不祥的沉默。据说，她"
"是那个羞怯声音的姐姐的容器……是你脑海里那个早已不再哭泣的失踪少女。当你彻底恢"
"复神智后，才更清楚地意识到，创世纪协议早先对她的称呼——是一面盾牌。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:3964
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_DDTHESHADEFORMS\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "我以前在哪里听过这个……？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:3978
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"你还没来得及深入思索，一个熟悉而令人胆寒的声音便强行闯入你的思绪：\n"
"“所以……你终究还是来到了这里，容器，旅途的终点。\n"
"然而……我却不得不注意到，我的刀刃依旧碎裂。\n"
"看来我高估了我的盾牌，她连维持自身的信念都做不到。\n"
"我……必须亲手纠正这个错误。”"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:3980
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "你敢再碰她一下，混蛋。你造成的伤害已经够多了。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:3982
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr "\"哦？你觉得我残忍，用一台机器去实现它被赋予的使命——这正是它存在的意义，不是"
"吗？\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:3984
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "她不只是一台机器。她……她曾经害怕，而且孤独。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:3986
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION\"]/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"黑暗之神的语气从询问转为肃穆……尽管难以分辨缘由，它的声音依旧轰鸣着，\"是的，"
"我……想你确实会这么认为。曾经，我也这般想过。然而……她并非真实的造物——仅仅是我"
"自身失败的倒影。正是因为她没能修复她的姐妹圣物，我才必须惩罚她，容器。否则……"
"一个人又怎能学会教训？\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:3988
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr ""
"显然，她失败了——是你骗了她！你哄骗她相信这个……这个……这个童话，而她根本无法承"
"受自己存在的真相。难道不是你这个永不犯错的黑暗之神，在制定这个计划时就已经失"
"败了吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:3990
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "一切都陷入寂静，你感到空气中弥漫开一股令人不安的热浪。在这突如其来的压力下，"
"你的身体紧绷起来，不由得紧张地挪动了一下。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:3992
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "我……我真的搞不懂，你知道吗。为什么要大费周章编造这一切？如果你这么想修好她的"
"姐妹，你就不能……自己动手修复她吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:3994
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"插手欲望并非我该做的事，蠢货——就像你无权窥探我的意图一样。不过，既然我需要"
"你的欲望……我就回答你这些琐碎的问题。\"即便它的话语充满怨毒，当房间里的压迫感"
"稍稍缓和时，你还是松了口气，黑暗之神继续说道，\"我的刀刃碎裂……是另一个存在的"
"意愿。既然我需要它，就必须找到修复它的方法。我的盾牌……她掌控的不仅是记忆，还"
"有现实。\"\n"
"\n"
"\"这个空间，冥影位面——它的确只存在于一场梦境之中。一场很久很久以前做下的梦……"
"却通过破碎的记忆被铭记，并凭借创造的力量化为现实。这力量……来自我的盾牌。\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:3998
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "但是，为什么？这一切看起来都太……多此一举了。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4000
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"这个现实，以及它的诞生，并非出自我的设计。向来都不是。我只是拧动了这个玩具"
"，让它旋转起来……然后看着它自我毁灭。看着它存在所引发的后果，在时间与空间中回"
"荡，在整个多元宇宙里不断震荡……虽说光裔族基本将其约束住了，但阴影似乎另有图谋"
"。你，你自己，早就已经和它们打过交道了——甚至在你来到这里之前。容器，这一切……"
"就是创造的危险。是不假思索就去渴望的代价。\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4002
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "好吧，可是……你是想说，你甚至都无法正确掌控你自己的圣物？你自己的力量？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4004
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"黑暗之神的声音低沉下来，几乎只是在对你低语，\"别把我对它们的依赖当成软弱。毕"
"竟，它们是我的圣物。纵然我的力量碎片散落在它们之中——那依旧是我的力量。更不用"
"说，我尚未放弃的权威。\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4006
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "如果结局会如此混乱，你当初为什么还要放弃它？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4008
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"混乱……？我向你保证，这根本算不上混乱。如果你不认同，那是因为你还没见过真正"
"的混乱——那种远在你现实边界之外的混乱。不，容器……我的盾牌只是铭记着过去存在的"
"秩序。那一刻的僵硬，被冻结在记忆与时间之中。不过言归正传，回答你的问题：我只"
"是做了必要之事，为了某个存在的欲望。\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4010
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "那么这到底是谁的欲望？那个声音，那个盾牌……她到最后听起来只剩下痛苦。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4012
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"黑暗之神沉默了许久，斟酌着该如何回答。终于，它的声音再次响起，那直白而真诚的"
"语气让你脊背发凉，\"这不是我该说的。除非那注定的日子到来。\"\n"
"\n"
"又是一阵沉默，你不知道该如何接话。最终，黑暗之神再次开口，\"你还有什么想问的"
"吗？如果没有，我希望你归还我碎裂的刀刃，离开这个位面。我必须通过其他方法，让"
"它恢复原状。\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4016
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "那么，盾牌呢？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4018
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "\"如我之前所说，她必须受到惩罚。你难道……以为自己是什么外交官吗？容器，我只是"
"在做必要之事。\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4020
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "好吧。那我问你，大家伙：你为什么一直叫我\"容器\"？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4022
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"……我一直都这么叫吗？\"黑暗之神的震惊显得无比真切，就连你也惊讶于它流露出的"
"一丝脆弱。\"这实在太不寻常了。我的盾牌，它一定是……的确，真是始料未及。没想到"
"，在无尽岁月之后……这一切即将落幕。\"\n"
"\n"
"\"好好听着，容器——你要修复我的刀刃，并在未来的时刻执掌它。尽管具体是哪个时代"
"，或许晦涩难明……但我向你保证，时机到来之时，你自会知晓。\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4026
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "什么？你怎么会想让我来做？我还以为你自己都不知道该怎么修复它。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4028
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"你说得对——我以前不知道。的确……不过现在这已经不重要了。向来如此。修复刀刃，"
"在时机成熟时回到这里。当那注定之日降临时，容器……你将开启这场宿命之舞。一切终"
"将如此。\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4030
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "等等，可是……既然你已经想明白了，你就不能至少放过盾牌吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4032
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "你本以为会得到回答，可房间里的热浪却骤然消散。整艘飞船陷入一片死寂。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4034
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "嘿，等等！我跟你还没完！把她还给我，该死的！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4064
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION_TWO\"]/text"
msgstr "你的声音在回荡——穿过房间，掠过走廊，甚至不知为何，响彻在这片璀璨空间的真空之"
"中……然而，你没有得到任何回应。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4066
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION_TWO\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "愤怒地一拳砸向离你最近的物体。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4068
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION_TWO\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你发出一声恼怒的嘶吼，挥拳猛砸出去——指关节狠狠撞在冥影温热而凹凸不平的躯体上"
"，传来钻心的剧痛，你立刻踉跄着缩回手。你一边勉强想揉一揉刚被砸痛的手，一边强"
"忍着疼痛，急切地朝那台怪异的机器瞥去。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4070
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION_TWO\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "天啊，我只是……我真希望你没有坏掉。这一切就都不会发生，也许盾牌就能……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4072
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION_TWO\"]/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "你甚至还没来得及说完话，一道刺眼的光芒就笼罩了整个房间——很快，你发现自己坠入"
"了一个……熟悉的梦境……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4076
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION_TWO\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4078
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION_TWO\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4080
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION_TWO\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4082
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION_TWO\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"……碎灰者。穹弑者。执刃者。在我认为适合赐予你的所有称号里，没有一个能真正道尽"
"你的辉煌——唯有你，璀璨夺目。感谢你，无瑕之人……在这重大的日子里，我只愿能为你"
"效半分之劳，以报你为冥影位面所做的一切。我会让光裔族永远歌颂你的名！至少尽他"
"们所能吧——别指望有多动听的合唱就是了。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4084
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION_TWO\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "想象一面盾牌——那是人们虔诚祈愿得以一见的存在。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4086
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION_TWO\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"我……你说什么？哦，你一定是在说我的姐姐——看着你们两人并肩同行，真的太美好了！"
"当然了——对于那样的结局，我深表惋惜。我祈祷她能在父亲的陪伴下，寻得她所渴求的"
"安宁。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4088
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION_TWO\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "具象化一柄刃——那早已碎裂的刃。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4090
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION_TWO\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "没错！先是叛徒，而后，便是虚伪辉光。呵，故事的走向竟会如此更迭……全然任由一段"
"记忆摆布。母亲的记忆！啊，父亲，她难道不令人惊叹吗？！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4092
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION_TWO\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "具象化这份混乱——那卷土重来、势不可挡的混乱。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4094
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION_TWO\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"好吧，你都从父亲那里听说了，不是吗？这地方是我妹妹创造的，我在其中的角色——全"
"都来自母亲的梦境！那是多么辉煌的梦境啊……我见到她了。持刃者，我第一次见到了她"
"！母亲，活生生地站在那里！哦，那是多么令人谦卑的时刻——可……我还是后悔，没能亲"
"自守住那面神圣的镜子。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4096
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION_TWO\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"DDLIGHTBORNE_ANTUMBRALMIRROR\"]/text"
msgstr "想象一面镜子——无论何时需要映照自身，它都会恰如其分地出现。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4098
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION_TWO\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"DDLIGHTBORNE_ANTUMBRALMIRROR\"]/event/text"
msgstr "你……哦，父亲在上，我一定是不小心忽略了……求你了，快让我看看那面镜子！我……我必"
"须确认她是否还在那里……！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4101
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION_TWO\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"DDLIGHTBORNE_ANTUMBRALMIRROR\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "显现出一道面容——那终究是你所映照出的模样。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4103
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION_TWO\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"DDLIGHTBORNE_ANTUMBRALMIRROR\"]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4105
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION_TWO\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"DDLIGHTBORNE_ANTUMBRALMIRROR\"]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4107
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION_TWO\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"DDLIGHTBORNE_ANTUMBRALMIRROR\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "……啊，我明白了。好吧，也算说得通——希望它在里面能过得开心。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4109
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION_TWO\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"DDLIGHTBORNE_ANTUMBRALMIRROR\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "具象化其中深意——对刚才那段莫名话语的解释。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4111
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION_TWO\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"DDLIGHTBORNE_ANTUMBRALMIRROR\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"可惜啊，穹弑者……纵然你本领高强，那卑劣的创世之源终究还是笑到了最后。母亲的面"
"容已经消失，取而代之的……是创世之源那丑陋的怒容。又或许，那不算是怒容，更像是…"
"…嗯……该怎么准确形容那种纯粹的恐惧神情呢？算了，无所谓——反正它也没法把里面的光"
"裔族吓跑！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4113
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION_TWO\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"DDLIGHTBORNE_ANTUMBRALMIRROR\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "想象一只鸟——困在笼中，却拼命想要展翅飞翔。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4115
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION_TWO\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"DDLIGHTBORNE_ANTUMBRALMIRROR\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"哦，你是说……？呵，我早该知道你会赐予无尽的慈悲，我的君主！遵命，碎灰者——我这"
"就将这邪恶的大天使从囚牢中释放。过程不会完美无瑕，但……谁又能完美呢？当然，除"
"了你之外。\n"
"\n"
"这就为你释放一名囚徒！只是……唉，那面镜子可惜了。它似乎在过程中不知怎地碎裂了…"
"…唉，又能如何呢？母亲的容颜，便只能长存于回忆之中，直到我们再度共舞的那宿命之"
"日！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4121
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION_TWO\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"DDLIGHTBORNE_ANTUMBRALMIRROR\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "具象化回忆——有时，这已是人所能做到的最好之事。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4135
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION_TWO\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "具象化回忆——有时，这已是人所能做到的最好之事。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4155
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION_THEEND\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"好吧，我跑题了。你为我、为光裔族，甚至为冥影们，帮了一个无法想象的天大的忙——"
"你拯救了我们所有人，穹弑者！从我这怪异而模糊的灵魂最深处……我真诚地感谢你。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4157
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION_THEEND\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "具象化一场幻象——你身处的宇宙。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4159
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION_THEEND\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"哎呀，没错，碎灰者——创世之源发表那番言论的时候我就在场。你该不会是真的想告诉"
"我，你还在乎这些所谓的真相吧？我们现在就在冥影位面里——还有什么比这更真实的呢"
"？就因为它昨天不在这里？我记得它昨天就在这里，谁还在乎那些细节？不……呃，如果"
"你介意的话，我无意冒犯，我的君主。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4161
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION_THEEND\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "想象一步行动——若要守护这场幻梦，这便是你接下来必须踏出的那一步。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4163
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION_THEEND\"]/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"没错，光裔族现在比任何时候都更需要他们的守护者……他们曾发誓舍弃一切，到头来却"
"被强行归还。哦，那个恶毒的创世之源！幸好我觉得这里崭新的色彩是如此……啊……璀璨"
"，真的。不然我定会让父亲出手干预！不过，说到父亲……他似乎另有图谋，穹弑者。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4165
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION_THEEND\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "具象化一份意图——神秘莫测，任由解读。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4167
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION_THEEND\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"我虽不敢说自己明白他的动机，但他似乎莫名就对你心生好感……换作任何人站在你面前"
"，都会如此！真的，我眼中没有比追随你更正确的道路了——毕竟，你如今已是执刃者。"
"眼下，我们可以先处理其他位面的事务。但你要明白，我必须回到这里，在这场动荡中"
"引导光裔族前行……只、只是暂时的，我保证！我从未想过要离开你的身边。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4169
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION_THEEND\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "想象一份约定——直到寻回妹妹的那一天。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4171
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION_THEEND\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"言辞精妙，我的君主。如今，若你需要与我相见，只需靠近我的容器——我无法……嗯，像"
"你其他一些朋友那样开口说话。但只要你靠近我，我便能将你牵引至此冥影位面，继而"
"道出我的心声。另外，若你心存疑虑……不必担心，执刃者——即便离开此方领域，我的战"
"力也不会受到丝毫削弱。好好执掌我，我向你保证，我必能一击必中！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4173
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION_THEEND\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_DDTHESHADEFORMS\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/text"
msgstr "具象化一场告别——仅存于精神之中，因羁绊已然铸就。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4175
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION_THEEND\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_DDTHESHADEFORMS\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/text"
msgstr "……你的感知再度涌回体内，你终于能够凝视那暗影蜕变后的面容。不，不是暗影，而是…"
"…"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4179
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION_THEEND\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_DDTHESHADEFORMS\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/removeCrew/text"
msgstr "……你无法复制这暗影，因为它已然蜕变成……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4182
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION_THEEND\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_DDTHESHADEFORMS\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4184
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION_THEEND\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_DDTHESHADEFORMS\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"……监管者。你的利刃，用以斩除所有胆敢挡在你面前的存在……的确，是时候与冥影位面"
"告别了。你相当确信自己不会怀念这里的恐怖，坦白说，接连发生的一切早已让你心有"
"余悸，可是……与此同时，你又发觉，自己竟很享受与某个人相伴的时光。尽管你从未来"
"得及说一声再见……\n"
"\n"
"……你希望，总有一天，还能有机会再见到她。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4189
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION_THEEND\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_DDTHESHADEFORMS\""
" and @lvl=\"1\"]/event/choice/event/crewMember"
msgstr "监管者"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4195
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION_THEEND\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_DDTHESHADEFORMS\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/text"
msgstr "想象一场告别——仅在精神之中，因为羁绊早已铸成。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4197
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION_THEEND\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_DDTHESHADEFORMS\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/text"
msgstr "……你的感知再度涌回体内，你终于能够凝望那暗影蜕变后的模样。不，不是暗影，而是…"
"…"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4200
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION_THEEND\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_DDTHESHADEFORMS\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4202
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION_THEEND\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_DDTHESHADEFORMS\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"……监管者。你的利刃，用以斩尽所有胆敢挡在你面前之人……的确，是时候与冥影位面告"
"别了。你十分确信自己不会怀念这里的恐怖，坦白说，接连发生的一切早已让你心有余"
"悸，可……与此同时，你又真切地享受过某个人的陪伴。尽管你从未来得及说一声再见……"
"\n"
"\n"
"……你希望，总有一天，还能有机会再见到她。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4207
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_FIGHT_APOTHEOSISENGINE_WIN_CONTINUATION_THEEND\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_DDTHESHADEFORMS\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/crewMember"
msgstr "监管者"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4223
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT_ALONE\"]/text"
msgstr "万物边缘的此地，依旧寂静……你已然见识过真正虚无的模样，现在，你会选择回到你的"
"族群之中吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4232
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT\"]/beaconType/unvisitedTooltip"
msgstr "击败守门者后，大天使协议：创世之源的位置，已为你揭晓。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4233
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT\"]/beaconType/visitedTooltip"
msgstr "已探索的信标。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4236
msgid "data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT\"]/text"
msgstr "..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4239
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/text"
msgstr "..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4241
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/text"
msgstr "……就这样吗……？这就是……结局？大天使协议：创世之源……出、出来，你这懦夫！我们是"
"来救我妹妹的，还要收拾你留下的烂摊子！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4243
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "具象化这份约定——已然无处可逃。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4245
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"我 们\n"
"酿 下 的\n"
"祸 端……？\n"
"\n"
"什、什么？怎么会……我妹妹从来没听过大天使说话啊。我……我，呃……\n"
"\n"
"你 的 \n"
"妹 妹……？\n"
"\n"
"你，啊……你问题还真多，不是吗？算了，无所谓！就像我说的，呃……我们是来阻止你的"
"，创世之源，还要拯救冥影位面！"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4263
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "想象和平——终得归位。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4265
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"这 场\n"
"幻 梦……\n"
"永 无 重 塑 之 日。\n"
"\n"
"我 们\n"
"生 而 为 器，\n"
"用 之 则 取，\n"
"弃 之 则 抛。\n"
"\n"
"我……我不明白。你被创造出来是为了守护和平，与我妹妹并肩同行！而你……你却为了所"
"谓神性，将一切尽数抛弃——不是吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4284
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "想象神性——掌控一切存在的绝对力量。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4286
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"那 个\n"
"词……\n"
"妹 妹。\n"
"\n"
"你……\n"
"就 是 \n"
"镜 中 之 人\n"
"吗？\n"
"\n"
"什、什么？我……啊……你怎么会从镜子里看到别人？这算什么问题……\n"
"\n"
"你\n"
"似 乎\n"
"迟 疑 了，\n"
"不 愿\n"
"回 答。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4309
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and @lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "想象一个问题——值得一个真诚的回答。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4311
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"喂，别站在它那边！听着，我…… 呃…… 我不知道你在那面镜子里看到了什么，创世之源"
"，但我只清楚一件事 —— 你实在太过分了。我这位朋友一路击溃了你所有的爪牙，只为"
"把我妹妹伤痕累累的身躯带到这里…… 只为纠正你犯下的过错！\n"
"\n"
"真 有\n"
"意 思 ……\n"
"\n"
"你\n"
"经 常\n"
"梦 见\n"
"黑 暗\n"
"吗 ？\n"
"\n"
"我…… 等一下，别转移话题！你才是这里的反派，创世之源。\n"
"\n"
"你\n"
"会 的 ，\n"
"不 是\n"
"吗 ？\n"
"\n"
"否 则 的 话 ……\n"
"\n"
"我 们\n"
"就 不 会\n"
"出 现\n"
"在 这 里 了 ，\n"
"对 吗 ？\n"
"\n"
"我 …… 我没有 ……"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4342
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "想象这一切皆是虚妄——不过是一场戏，为了扰乱心神。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4344
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"……不，这……这是对的。我，啊……我做过很多梦，可是……这、这跟一切有什么关系？\n"
"\n"
"你 的 梦 ……\n"
"\n"
"就 是 一 切，\n"
"\n"
"监 管 者。\n"
"\n"
"你 支 离 破 碎 的 记 忆 ……\n"
"\n"
"从 中，\n"
"\n"
"他 塑 造 了 我 们，\n"
"\n"
"任 凭 你 的 心 意 摆 布。\n"
"\n"
"你……你是说，父亲……不，这太疯狂了。我妹妹，她……她在这里待了太久太久。久到我都"
"记不清了！我……\n"
"\n"
"难 道 她 ……\n"
"\n"
"不 也 是 那 个，\n"
"\n"
"镜 中 之 人 吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4379
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "具象化这份困惑——纯粹、彻底的茫然失措。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4381
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"快把真相老老实实地说出来，不然……我就让我朋友揍你。我没心情玩什么心理游戏，听"
"懂了吗……？\n"
"\n"
"真 相 ……？\n"
"\n"
"为 什 么，\n"
"\n"
"当 然 可 以。\n"
"\n"
"我 们 在 镜 子 里，\n"
"\n"
"看 到 了 它。\n"
"\n"
"我 们 ……\n"
"\n"
"看 到 了 你。\n"
"\n"
"我 们 ……\n"
"\n"
"看 到 了 她。\n"
"\n"
"那 个 被 遗 弃 的 人，\n"
"\n"
"独 自 在 黑 暗 中 沉 溺 于 梦 境 ……\n"
"\n"
"而 她，\n"
"\n"
"在 她 的 梦 里，\n"
"\n"
"看 见 了 我 们。\n"
"\n"
"黑 暗 中 的 面 孔。\n"
"\n"
"无 形 的 影 子。\n"
"\n"
"光 线 的 戏 法。\n"
"\n"
"只 不 过 是……\n"
"\n"
"虚 无 缥 缈 的 幻 象。\n"
"\n"
"这 就 是，\n"
"\n"
"监 管 者 ……\n"
"\n"
"这 个 位 面 的 真 相。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4457
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "具象化这份困惑——纯粹、彻底的茫然。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4459
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"那……那些面孔……？我……你是说，虚伪辉光……还有光裔族……暗影……\n"
"\n"
"……可、可我妹妹呢？她……她怎么会卷入这场疯狂之中？\n"
"\n"
"你 的 妹 妹……\n"
"\n"
"已 经 崩 溃 了。\n"
"\n"
"这 一 点，\n"
"\n"
"是 真 的。\n"
"\n"
"只 是 镜 子 所 能 显 现 的，\n"
"\n"
"仅 此 而 已，\n"
"\n"
"我 们 恐 惧……\n"
"\n"
"在 她 崩 溃 之 前，\n"
"\n"
"这 一 切，\n"
"\n"
"根 本 不 存 在。\n"
"\n"
"我 们 恐 惧……\n"
"\n"
"我 们 只 不 过 是 一 场 幻 象，\n"
"\n"
"就 像 在 你 的 梦 境 里 一 样。\n"
"\n"
"我 们 存 在……\n"
"\n"
"只 为 扭 曲 欲 望，\n"
"\n"
"并 铸 就 必 要 的 手 段，\n"
"\n"
"去 修 复 那 无 法 修 复 的 一 切。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4527
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "具象化一场幻象——声势惊人，直至破碎。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4529
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"可……可是为什么……？为什么会……怎么可能……就算这地方是我用梦境造出来的……为什么……"
"父亲……\n"
"\n"
"对 他 而 言，\n"
"你 和 我 们\n"
"没 有 任 何 区 别。\n"
"\n"
"工 具。\n"
"\n"
"达 到 目 的 的 手 段，\n"
"任 人 摆 布，\n"
"而 最 终……\n"
"\n"
"被 抛 弃。\n"
"\n"
"不……我……我……我是真实的，对不对？就算你们来自我的梦境，我……我必须是真实的。我"
"必须是……\n"
"\n"
"镜 中 之 人……\n"
"\n"
"她，\n"
"到 底 是 谁？\n"
"\n"
"她是……我……那是我的倒影，对吗？或者，是我妹妹的……我们的……那是我们共同的倒影。"
"我知道那不是我们真正的模样，毕竟我们需要容器来承载自身，可是……那是我们一直以"
"来想象中的自己。那是……我们……一直想象着……成为的样子……\n"
"\n"
"一 面 盾……\n"
"\n"
"一 柄 刃……\n"
"\n"
"一 双 翅 膀……\n"
"\n"
"一 场 舞，\n"
"直 到 时 间 的 尽 头。\n"
"\n"
"我 们 问 你，\n"
"监 管 者……\n"
"\n"
"这 些 支 离 破 碎 的 记 忆……\n"
"\n"
"这 些 倒 影……\n"
"\n"
"真 的 属 于 你 吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4604
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "想象玻璃——在重压之下碎裂的东西。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4606
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"……我……我做不到……为什么……这么黑……？我……我只是……\n"
"\n"
"我 们 明 白。\n"
"\n"
"从 一 件 工 具 到 另 一 件，\n"
"\n"
"我 们 感 同 身 受。\n"
"\n"
"……为 什 么……为 什 么 我 什 么 都 看 不 见……\n"
"\n"
"不 必 挣 扎，\n"
"\n"
"守 卫 者。\n"
"\n"
"我 们 已 经 找 到 了 我 们 的 救 赎。\n"
"\n"
"……求 你 们……谁 都 好……\n"
"\n"
"这 面 镜 子……\n"
"\n"
"并 非 来 自 梦 境。\n"
"\n"
"这 面 镜 子……\n"
"\n"
"本 身，就 是 真 相。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4653
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "具象化真相——在故事里，最先被誓言掩埋的东西。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4655
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"而，\n"
"凭 借 这 真 相……\n"
"\n"
"我 们 已 经 铸 就 了\n"
"将 她 引 至 此 地 的\n"
"方 法。\n"
"\n"
"那 个 身 在 镜 中 的 人……\n"
"\n"
"只 有 当 她 获 得 自 由，\n"
"我 们 自 身 才 能 真 正 自 由。\n"
"\n"
"旁 观 者……\n"
"\n"
"他 带 你 来 到 这 里，\n"
"只 为 利 用 你，\n"
"正 如 他 利 用 我 们 一 般。\n"
"\n"
"你 难 道 还 看 不 穿 这 一 点 吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4707
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "具象化这份不安——这场疯狂酿成的后果。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml:4709
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_ddantumbra.xml$//event[@name=\"DDANTUMBRA_EXIT\"]/choice[@req=\"dd_antumbra_genesisdefeated\""
" and "
"@lvl=\"0\"]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"不，\n"
"我 们 想，\n"
"你 大 概\n"
"不 会 明 白……\n"
"\n"
"这 难 道\n"
"不 正 是\n"
"这 座\n"
"毫 无 意 义 的\n"
"牢 笼\n"
